item.title: Help! i got moparscape, its called Moparscape Private Server Client 2!
item.dc:creator: @Rare_z Rare z
item.description:
@Rare_z wrote:

If it says “Error connecting to server, must be offline” it means that the server you’re trying to connect to is offline. You simply try another server, also check your port… Some servers require you to change it (Click file on the left-top side then add port… type port and ok).
